IATF resolutions URLs from the Official Gazette

Source: R/data.R
iatfLinksGazette.Rd

IATF resolutions URLs from the Official Gazette

iatfLinksGazette

Format

A tibble with 53 rows and 7 columns:

id

Unique identifier

title

Title of resolution

date

Date resolution released. Format <YYYY-MM-DD>

source

Issuing agency. IATF by default

type

Type of issuance. Resolution by default

link

Absolute URL of IATF resolution

checked

Date (in <YYYY-MM_DD> format) information was extracted. Default is Sys.Date()

Source

https://www.officialgazette.gov.ph/. Updated as of 16 June 2020.
